# 09 Incident Response and Breach Notification

## Intent
Detect, triage, contain, and report incidents within legal and operational timelines.

## Mandatory
- Maintain incident severity taxonomy and on-call escalation path.
- Capture immutable evidence trail for incident decisions/actions.
- Define notification workflow for regulator/user obligations.
- Track GDPR 72-hour notification clock for reportable breaches.

## HIPAA/GDPR Handling
- Trigger compliance/legal review when PHI or personal-data compromise is suspected.
- Record breach-scope assessment, affected populations, and mitigation actions.

## Release Blockers
- No tested incident runbook.
- No owner for breach reporting decisions.
